(7327, 1397, 'Newsdirectory', 'Newsdirectory is a comprehensive and searchable guide to the world\'s English-language online media. Currently over 8,000 newspapers and magazines are listed, as well as more than 1,000 U.S. television broadcasters.', 'http://www.newsdirectory.com/', 'http://ask.elibrary.com/search.asp?refid=NEWSD&datetype=all&srcmags=checked&srcnews=checked&srcbooks=checked&srctvrad=checked&query={$formKeywords}', NULL, 9),
