(6724, 1283, 'Biospace', 'BioSpace is a provider of web-based resources and information to the life science industry. For 20 years BioSpace has helped to accelerate communication and discovery among business and scientific leaders in the biopharmaceutical market. With a well-established site infrastructure and loyal online audience of over 1 million unique monthly visitors, BioSpace.com offers an unparalleled distribution channel for recruitment, investment, product, event and other life science industry messages.', 'http://www.biospace.com', 'http://www.biospace.com/Default.aspx', 'ctl00$DropDownList1=News&ctl00$TextBox1={$formKeywords}', 0),
